# Sensitive files - NEVER commit
**/.ssh/id_*
**/.ssh/*.pem
**/.ssh/known_hosts
**/*.key
**/*.pem

# Credentials
**/.netrc
**/.npmrc
**/.pypirc
**/.htpasswd
**/credentials*
**/service-account*.json
**/*serviceAccountKey*.json
**/gcloud-key.json
**/*token*
**/*secret*
# secrets.md is the secrets-hygiene rule doc, not a secret — keep it tracked.
!packages/agents/.agents/rules/secrets.md
**/.env
**/.env.*

# Local overrides
*.local
.local/
**/rules/local.md
**/AGENTS.local.md
**/config.local.toml
**/.vagrant/

# OS junk
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Editor
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.idea/
.vscode/
